Now my favorite example is
a company called CarbonCure,

01:18:27.200 --> 01:18:31.330
they inject co2 as the
cement is being mixed,

01:18:31.330 --> 01:18:32.770
that creates...

01:18:33.880 --> 01:18:35.530
Here's that chemistry right here.

01:18:36.480 --> 01:18:37.857
