and it makes it a solid limestone,

01:18:40.420 --> 01:18:43.730
it turns out that means
you need less concrete.

01:18:43.730 --> 01:18:48.400
So the cost of using carbon
cure, you can recover

01:18:48.400 --> 01:18:51.293
