the concrete is stronger.

01:18:52.150 --> 01:18:54.350
And now you've taken
co2 that would have been

01:18:54.350 --> 01:18:58.690
in the atmosphere and instead
it's in your concrete.

01:18:58.690 --> 01:18:59.973
Yes?

